<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sys_script"><sys_script action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><abort_action>false</abort_action><access>package_private</access><action_delete>false</action_delete><action_insert>false</action_insert><action_query>false</action_query><action_update>true</action_update><active>false</active><add_message>false</add_message><advanced>true</advanced><change_fields>false</change_fields><client_callable>false</client_callable><collection>u_kpi</collection><condition/><description/><execute_function>false</execute_function><filter_condition table="u_kpi">u_teamsVALCHANGES^EQ<item endquery="false" field="u_teams" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="VALCHANGES" or="false" value=""/><item endquery="true" field="" goto="false" newquery="false" operator="=" or="false" value=""/></filter_condition><is_rest>false</is_rest><message/><name>CreateKPIResponsible</name><order>100</order><priority>100</priority><rest_method/><rest_method_text/><rest_service/><rest_service_text/><rest_variables/><role_conditions/><script><![CDATA[(function executeRule(current, previous /*null when async*/ ) {

    // Add your code here
    var teams = current.u_teams.split(",");
    gs.info("Riham: current: " + teams);
    var kpi_responsible = new GlideRecord('u_kpi_responsible');
    var previousTeams = previous.u_teams.split(",");
    gs.info("Riham: previous: " + previousTeams);
    for (var i = 0; i < teams.length; i++) {

        if (previousTeams.contains(teams[i])) {
            gs.info("Riham: found: " + teams[i]);
        } else {
            kpi_responsible.initialize();
            kpi_responsible.u_kpi = current.sys_id;
            kpi_responsible.u_team = teams[i];
            kpi_responsible.insert();
        }

    }

})(current, previous);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>riham.ahmed</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-05-01 14:55:37</sys_created_on><sys_domain>global</sys_domain><sys_domain_path>/</sys_domain_path><sys_id>ab61395bfbfd0e10b6d6fa71beefdc9c</sys_id><sys_mod_count>7</sys_mod_count><sys_name>CreateKPIResponsible</sys_name><sys_overrides/><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_ab61395bfbfd0e10b6d6fa71beefdc9c</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>riham.ahmed</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-05-02 08:54:36</sys_updated_on><template/><when>after</when></sys_script><sys_translated_text action="delete_multiple" query="documentkey=ab61395bfbfd0e10b6d6fa71beefdc9c"/></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_security_acl"><sys_security_acl action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><admin_overrides>true</admin_overrides><advanced>true</advanced><condition/><description>Default access control on u_kpi</description><local_or_existing>Local</local_or_existing><name>u_kpi</name><operation display_value="read">read</operation><script><![CDATA[asnwer = true;
if (gs.hasRole('team_manager')) {
	asnwer = false;
    var teams = current.u_teams.toString().split(",");
    for (var i = 0; i < teams.length; i++) {
        var teamGR = new GlideRecord("u_team");
        teamGR.get(teams[i]);
		gs.info("Riham: "+teamGR.u_manager);
        if (teamGR.u_manager == gs.getUserID()) {
			asnwer = true;
			break;
        }
    }
} else {
	asnwer = true;
}]]></script><security_attribute/><sys_class_name>sys_security_acl</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>riham.ahmed</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-05-01 09:18:04</sys_created_on><sys_id>63a4a413fbb50e10b6d6fa71beefdcf6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>4</sys_mod_count><sys_name>u_kpi</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_security_acl_63a4a413fbb50e10b6d6fa71beefdcf6</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>riham.ahmed</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-05-05 13:00:52</sys_updated_on><type display_value="record">record</type></sys_security_acl></record_update>
